Package: sddm-conf
Architecture: any
Depends: polkitd, sddm, ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Configuration editor for SDDM
 Configuration editor for SDDM similar to sddm-config-editor, but written in
 C++. Requires polkit to save settings.
